channel.title: The project named Ascension
channel.description:
Hello, i'm johannes. i'm currently working on a project called "Ascension". We're testing out the engine "Unity 3d" The engine supports "Java,C# and some other languages. We are currently looking for JAVA coders. And modelers.
Website :: *
We have background storys and class information done. it is just to follow. Why would i like to join this project? Well, we have a big community at *, Most of them there will try it out. Atm we have 400k visitors from all times. The project will be a smaller mmo. We will make a simple logg in and so you can go fight each other and stuff. This project will have great graphics.(Have)
You can check out the graphics on "Unity 3ds site" We will make it 3rd person and we have a UI already. So if you want to join. please send me a massage.
----------- I know you all might think, This is his first post, And he has almost no rep. Well i've been coding moparscape servers for over 5 years. And i can make sure there is nothing that can go wrong. If you have any questions just ask them and i will answer.
Bye :):)
